==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Fuzzy
<hw>Fuzz"y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[See <er>Fuzz</er>,
<pos>n.</pos>]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not firmly woven; that
ravels.</def> <altsp>[Written also <asp>fozy</asp>.]</altsp>
<mark>[Prov. Eng.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Furnished with fuzz; having fuzz; like fuzz; <as>as,
the <ex>fuzzy</ex> skin of a peach</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>-fy</ent>⟦br⟧
